title: 2016 Superstar Club
itunes:title: 2016 Superstar Club
description:
A room full of heroes -- Dan Hanzus, Gregg Rosenthal, Chris Wesseling and Marc Sessler – breakdown the latest NFL news including Dallas Cowboys running back Darren McFadden's injury, plus, Philadelphia Eagles defensive end Fletcher Cox and Denver Broncos linebacker Brandon Marshall's extensions. Also, the heroes reveal who made it into the 2016 Superstar Club and who fell out.
